  "id": "tsk-0133-fix-parameter-preservation-on-replan-remaining-count",
  "key": "TSK-0133",
  "title": "Fix Parameter Preservation on Replan (Remaining Count)",
  "description": "Research Report R2-003 (Confidence 93%, High). Audit correction (SteveBot 2026-06-26): TargetCount IS preserved because `_currentGoal` (the original GenericGatherGoal) is never replaced during replan cycles. The original goal object is used for all PlanAsync calls. `GenericGatherGoal.IsComplete` correctly accounts for already-gathered inventory.\n\nHowever, there is a real efficiency issue: the decomposer always generates a FULL gather plan (e.g., gather 64 logs) even when the inventory already has 60. The bot may queue unnecessary mine actions before `IsComplete` gates completion. `ReplanGoalContext`/`ReplanAsync` exist but are NOT wired into the production dispatch loop — only `PlanAsync` with the original goal is used.\n\nRevised fix:\n1. In `AgentBackgroundService.DispatchActionsAsync` (line ~1358), before calling `planner.PlanAsync(_currentGoal, ...)`, compute a remaining-target version of the goal:\n   - For `IItemSpecGoal`: clone with `TargetCount = max(0, originalTarget - inventoryCount)`\n   - For `GenericGatherGoal`: same computation\n   - For `CraftItemGoal`: same computation\n2. Use the remaining-count goal for planning, but keep `_currentGoal` as the original for `IsComplete` checks.\n3. Alternatively: wire `ReplanGoalContext` with the original goal into a new `PlanForReplan` method that decomposers can use to generate remaining-count plans.\n4. Add regression tests:\n   - Gather 5/10 logs → replan should request 5 more (not 10)\n   - Craft 3/8 planks → replan should request 5 more (not 8)\n   - Build with partial inventory → remaining materials only\n\nFiles:\n- AgentBackgroundService.cs:1358 (DispatchActionsAsync — PlanAsync call)\n- AgentBackgroundService.cs:228 (SetGoal — preserves _currentGoal)\n- Agent.Planning/Goals/GenericGatherGoal.cs:22-39 (IsComplete)\n- Agent.Planning/Decomposition/GatherGoalDecomposer.cs:40-56 (Decompose — passes full TargetCount)\n- Agent.Core/Models/ReplanGoalContext.cs (exists but not wired)\n- Agent.Planning/Router/PlannerRouter.cs:127-139 (ReplanAsync)\n\nSource: research-MemorySmith.Agent Codebase Audit Sprint-35, Council Addendum 2026-06-26. Code audit correction: SteveBot 2026-06-26.,
